", "bbox": [1122.0, 1041.5, 1171.6, 1069.6]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [93.8, 1080.1, 115.5, 1104.8]}, {"text": "Includes approximately 2.1 million acres in California, the large majority of which are net fee mineral interests.", "bbox": [131.3, 1080.1, 834.3, 1104.8]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [93.8, 1101.4, 115.5, 1126.1]}, {"text": "Acres spaced or assigned to productive wells.", "bbox": [131.3, 1101.4, 425.9, 1126.1]}, {"text": "(c)", "bbox": [93.8, 1122.6, 114.7, 1147.3]}, {"text": "Total acres in which interests are held.", "bbox": [131.3, 1122.6, 377.5, 1147.3]}, {"text": "(d)", "bbox": [93.8, 1143.9, 115.5, 1168.6]}, {"text": "Sum of the fractional interests owned based on working interests, or interests under PSCs and other economic arrangements.", "bbox": [131.3, 1143.9, 938.5, 1168.6]}, {"text": "(e)", "bbox": [93.8, 1165.1, 115.5, 1189.8]}, {"text": "Acres on which wells have not been drilled or completed to a point that would permit the production of commercial quantities of oil and gas, regardless of whether the", "bbox": [131.3, 1165.1, 1185.3, 1189.8]}, {"text": "acreage contains proved reserves.", "bbox": [131.3, 1186.4, 354.0, 1211.1]}, {"text": "Occidental’s investment in developed and undeveloped acreage comprises numerous concessions, blocks and leases.  Work", "bbox": [127.1, 1229.3, 1186.5, 1254.2]}, {"text": "programs are designed to ensure that the exploration potential of any property is fully evaluated before expiration.  In some instances,", "bbox": [93.8, 1251.8, 1186.5, 1276.7]}, {"text": "Occidental may elect to relinquish acreage in advance of the contractual expiration date if the evaluation process is complete and", "bbox": [93.8, 1274.3, 1186.5, 1299.2]}, {"text": "there is not a business basis for extension.  In cases where additional time may be required to fully evaluate acreage, Occidental has", "bbox": [93.8, 1296.8, 1186.5, 1321.7]}, {"text": "generally been successful in obtaining extensions.  Scheduled lease and concession expirations for undeveloped acreage over the", "bbox": [93.8, 1319.3, 1186.5, 1344.2]}, {"text": "next three years are not expected to have a material adverse impact on Occidental.", "bbox": [93.8, 1341.8, 784.7, 1366.7]}]}